Wolfblade:

"Oh hum, business as usual around here. Never do I get to smell the
mech fluid running on the ground in the morning. OH well, let's go and
get these bots and bring them back. Duty calls and all that stuff." 
She was hungry for battle, so much that she could almost taste it.
Being coopled up in this base with a bot whom her spark wanted more
than her own life, and yet, he was too soft to choose between her and
the other femmebot. But putting her feelings aside, she still let her
spark melt when he was around.  Once more she told herself to get her
programs fixed later on. Yet she somehow never got around to that.
With a seductive smile on her face, "Shall we go save someone?"
